text: Juban may refer to: * Juban, Iran, a village in Gilan Province, Iran * Juban, Sorsogon, a municipality in the Philippines * Juban, Shkodër, a settlement in Albania * Jewban or Juban, a Jewish Cuban * Azabu-Jūban, in Minato, Tokyo, Japan ==See also== * Juba (disambiguation), of whose various meanings "Juban" may be the adjective form
title: Juban
